org.gvsig.fmap.dal.feature.spi

Interface FeatureStoreProvider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataStoreProvider, Disposable, DynObject
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FeatureCacheProvider
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFeatureStoreProvider, AbstractMemoryStoreProvider, CSVStoreProvider, DBFStoreProvider, DGNStoreProvider, DWGStoreProvider, DXFStoreProvider, GMLDataStoreProvider, GPEStoreProvider, H2StoreProvider, JDBCStoreProvider, JDBCStoreProviderWriter, JExcelStoreProvider, MemoryStoreProvider, OGRDataStoreProvider, OGRStoreProvider, PostgreSQLStoreProvider, SeismicStoreProvider, SHPStoreProvider, WFSStoreProvider

    public interface FeatureStoreProvider
extends DataStoreProvider
    Interface for all feature based data providers.

    A FeatureStoreProvier must have a contructor like this:

    FeatureStoreProvider(DataStoreParameters, FeatureStoreProviderServices)
